snippet: Ramon Dominguez, the nation’s leading rider, sustained a fractured skull after being involved in a spill in the seventh race at Aqueduct Racetrack on Friday, his agent said
abstract: Ramon Dominguez, nation's leading jockey, sustains fractured skull after being involved in a spill at Aqueduct Racetrack.
lead_paragraph: Ramon Dominguez, the nation’s leading rider, sustained a fractured skull after being involved in a spill in the seventh race at Aqueduct Racetrack on Friday, his agent said
